    "title": "AWS App Mesh",
    "description": "AWS App Mesh is a service mesh based on the Envoy proxy that makes it easy to monitor and\n         control microservices. App Mesh standardizes how your microservices communicate, giving you\n         end-to-end visibility and helping to ensure high availability for your applications.",
